"보라카이":{en:{description:"Boracay is a tiny island with one of the world's best beaches — 4km of powdery white sand on the Western Visayas.",spots:{"화이트 비치":{"name":null,"desc":"4km of powder-fine white sand regularly ranked among the world's best beaches."},"불라복":{"name":null,"desc":"Boracay's kitesurfing and windsurfing mecca with consistent winds and shallow turquoise waters."}}}},
