"카이로":{en:{description:"Cairo is the sprawling capital of Egypt, where the Pyramids of Giza meet medieval Islamic architecture and vibrant bazaars.",spots:{"기자 피라미드":{"name":null,"desc":"The last surviving Ancient Wonder — three pyramids and the Great Sphinx standing for 4,500 years."},"이집트 박물관":{"name":null,"desc":"Home to Tutankhamun's golden mask and 120,000+ ancient Egyptian artifacts."},"칸엘칼릴리 바자르":{"name":null,"desc":"Cairo's medieval bazaar since the 14th century. A labyrinth of shops selling spices, perfumes, and crafts."},"이슬람 지구":{"name":null,"desc":"UNESCO historic Cairo with stunning mosques, madrasas, and the Citadel of Saladin."}}}},
