"알가르브":{en:{description:"The Algarve is Portugal's southern coast — dramatic sea caves, golden cliffs, and some of Europe's finest beaches.",spots:{"베나길 동굴":{"name":null,"desc":"Iconic sea cave with a natural skylight hole in the ceiling, accessible only by boat or kayak."},"프라이아 다 마린야":{"name":null,"desc":"Stunning beach surrounded by golden limestone cliffs and natural arches."}}}},
