"에게르":{en:{description:"Eger is a charming Hungarian town famous for its baroque old town, castle, thermal baths, and the Valley of Beautiful Women wines.",spots:{"에게르 성":{"name":null,"desc":"Medieval fortress that heroically resisted Ottoman siege in 1552. Museum inside with panoramic town views."},"세프아소뇨크 볼지(미녀의 계곡)":{"name":null,"desc":"Valley of wine cellars where you can sample Egri Bikavér (Bull's Blood) and other local wines."}}}},
